---
name: structured-output
description: A prompt with structured output schema
model:
  id: gpt-4o
  provider: openai
  apiType: chat
  connection:
    kind: key
    apiKey: ${env:OPENAI_API_KEY:test-key}
inputs:
  - name: topic
    kind: string
    default: quantum computing
outputs:
  - name: summary
    kind: string
    description: A brief summary
    required: true
  - name: keyPoints
    kind: array
    description: Key points about the topic
    required: true
  - name: confidence
    kind: number
    description: Confidence score 0-1
---
system:
You are a research assistant that returns structured data.

user:
Summarize {{topic}} for me.
